1. *Pričali* smo o knjigama. (We talked about books.) 
2. *Pričala* je sa njim celu noć. (She talked with him all night.)
3. *Priča* se da će biti velike promene. (It is said that there will be big changes.)
4. Oni su *pričali* o gradu. (They talked about the city.)
5. Ona je *pričala* o njenim budućim planovima. (She was talking about her future plans.)
6. Oni su *pričali* o njenom povratku. (They talked about her return.)